    Table Type:

    Domain Extensions which support this table

    • aquarelle
    Policy Statement:
    A Unicode string MUST NOT contain "--" (two consecutive hyphens) in the third- and fourth-character positions and MUST NOT start or end with a "-" (hyphen). See RFC5891, Section 4.2.3.1.
